Changelog for Pegg 0.23
------------------------

	Pegg 0.23 - Linux support for Casio label printers.

	Copyright (c) 2003,2004 Daniel Amkreutz, <daniel.amkreutz@tu-harburg.de>
                  (c) 2004 Alex Perry, <alex@pamurray.com>
    
